alari qanday?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"So'mda: yillik 20-26%. Dollarda: 4-7%. Yevroda: 2-4%. Bank va muddatga bog'liq."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Oylik kapitalizatsiya yoki oxirida to'lov yaxshiroqmi?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Oylik kapitalizatsiya foydaliroq: nominal stavkaga qarab samarali stavkani 1-3% ga oshiradi."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Omonatlar sug'urtalanganmi?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Ha, barcha jismoniy shaxs omonatlari Kafolatlash fondi tomonidan bir omonatchiga bir bankda 200 mln so'mgacha kafolatlangan."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Omonat daromadi soliqqa tortiladimi?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Ha, depozit foizlari rezidentlar uchun 5% (norezidentlar uchun 10%) JShShSga tortiladi. Bank foizlarni to'lashda soliqni avtomatik ravishda ushlab qoladi."}}]},{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"TechArticle","headline":"Depozitlarni solishtirish","description":"O'zbekistonning turli banklari omonat shartlarini solishtiring. Parametrlaringiz bo'yicha eng foydali depozitni toping.","url":"https://calk.uz/uz/calculator/depozitlarni-solishtirish","datePublished":"2025-04-02","dateModified":"2026-02-16","author":{"@type":"Person","@id":"https://calk.uz/#founder","name":"Konstantin Yakovlev","alternateName":"Константин Яковлев","url":"https://calk.uz/uz/author/konstantin-yakovlev","jobTitle":"Calk.UZ loyihasi asoschisi va rahbari","image":"https://calk.uz/og/author-konstantin.jpg"},"reviewedBy":{"@type":"Organization","name":"Calk.UZ","url":"https://calk.uz"},"publisher":{"@type":"Organization","@id":"https://calk.uz/#organization","name":"Calk.UZ","url":"https://calk.uz","logo":{"@type":"ImageObject","url":"https://calk.uz/favicon.svg"}},"inLanguage":"uz","mainEntityOfPage":"https://calk.uz/uz/calculator/depozitlarni-solishtirish"},{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"HowTo","name":"Depozitlarni solishtirishdan qanday foydalanish","description":"Depozitlarni solishtirishd